page.title: 10ME JOANNA NOBBS AGE 11
page.content: I live near{LIFTON}in {DEVON}at a farm called {LOWER CROSS}. I like living here it is very nice. We have got some cows.I used to live in {ESSEX}near {LONDON}in a village called {WEST HORNDON}. We moved 2 and a half years ago. I liked living in {ESSEX}but i like it best in {DEVON}.I miss the familly alot.{5 live in our house}.When i grow up i would like to be a {ARCHITECT}or work in a {BANK}. I would like to live in the country side in a cottage with a thatched roof and have about 50 acres.
